		<div class="navigation">
			<div class="alignleft">&laquo; <a href="http://ottopress.com/2012/theme-customizer-part-deux-getting-rid-of-options-pages/" rel="prev">Theme Customizer Part Deux: Getting rid of Options pages</a></div>
