	<div itemprop="text"><p>Hi Gihan,</p>
<p>Add a function called &#8216;enqueue&#8217; to your Slider_Control class that contain the wp_enqueue_script calls.</p>
<p>Like:</p>
<p><code>public function enqueue()<br />
{<br />
  wp_enqueue_script( 'jquery-ui-slider' );<br />
}</code></p>
</div>

