	<div itemprop="text"><p>Hi Otto,</p>
<p>I am in the process of creating a WP custom theme and I will use theme customisation to give the user the posibility to change some elements in the theme. Several elements changable will be CSS elements which based on the standard implementation of theme customizer will be inserted in the page header.</p>
