		<div id="div-comment-11934" class="comment-body">
		<div class="comment-author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
	<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/5d4dcca214e3c6f4055fa37e79dce30f?s=48&amp;d=retro&amp;r=X' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />	<cite itemprop="name"><a itemprop='url' href='http://www.fillim.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Dan Solo</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>	</div>

	<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a itemprop="url" href="http://ottopress.com/2012/making-a-custom-control-for-the-theme-customizer/comment-page-1/#comment-11934">
		<time itemprop="dateCreated" datetime="2013-07-23T18:12:04+00:00">July 23, 2013 at 6:12 pm</time></a>	</div>

	<div itemprop="text"><p>haha&#8230; Sorted it out.<br />
If anyone is interested change
<pre class="brush: php; title: ; notranslate" title="">echo get_theme_mod( 'textarea_setting', 'default_value' ).&quot;\n&quot;;</pre>
<p> to
<pre class="brush: php; title: ; notranslate" title="">&lt;?php echo wpautop(get_theme_mod( 'textarea_setting', 'default_value' )).&quot;\n&quot;; ?&gt;</pre>
</div>

